Install a few python libraies in your system and/or virtualenv::

    $ pip install pylint pep8 pyflakes nose nose_machineout

Clone::
    $ git clone git://github.com/rizumu/rizumu-emacs.git ~/.emacs.d

Takeoff::
    $ emacs takeoff.py

